nitial investment in sss of  million followed by another  million which the selfstorage operator will use to fund growth opportunities the source reported sss intends to acquire individual storage facilities and small to midsized portfolios in secondary markets while considering new developments in major and small markets the selfstorage company is expected to retain its current leadership neither bam nor sss officials have commented publicly on the acquisition although the asset manager alluded to the transaction in its interim thirdquarter  financial report the company “committed or deployed” about  billion in various investments during the quarter “we also agreed to acquire a north american selfstorage company with  locations and an enterprise value of  million and hope this can be a cornerstone investment for growth of a larger national business” bam officials said in the report the ipe article attributes the  us selfstorage facilities to sss although the operator reported a total portfolio of  owned and managed facilities last fall during the collection of data for the  inside selfstorage topoperators list an annual ranking of the top  operators in the industry by square footage sss is no  in the latest ranking with a footprint of nearly  million square feet headquartered in orlando fla sss operates a portfolio spanning  states and puerto rico the company was founded in  by kurt o’brien who serves as president the deal was initially reported by the orange county employees retirement system which has been considering an investment into the partners ii fund bam has raised about  billion for the fund with a goal of  billion according to the source the fund is targeting opportunities in australia brazil europe and north america the sss acquisition is part of  billion in deals bam has committed to the fund the source reported bam currently has  billion in assets under management according to its website it owns and operates assets with a focus on infrastructure private equity property and renewable energy the company offers a range of public and private investment products and services and is colisted on the new york toronto and euronext stock exchanges sources brookfield asset management website ipe real estate brookfield am lines up m us selfstorage deal email tweet comments comments similar articles selfstorage software storage commander partners with first american payment systems source capital acquires selfstorage accesscontrol company pti security systems selfstorage building manufacturer butler introduces electronic erection drawing system s introduces dualguard snowretention system for standingseam metal roofs superior self storage of wichita ks gets zoning approval despite residential opposition latest articles investing in selfstorage gauging property potential author mark helm establish dollarspermonth goals for your selfstorage business former general counsel for selfstorage operator lifestorage joins wzem law firm apple self storage opens  new facilities in mississauga canada selfstorage software provider sitelink enhances cloud solution for uk market other resources inside selfstorage international  inside selfstorage boatrv storage  please enable javascript to view the comments powered by disqus comments powered by disqus store products storage world analyzer software version  selfstorage custom caprates report iss poll in your opinion whats the most important ability to be granted in a state selfstorage lien law subscribe inside selfstorage first name last name email resources  case study what happens when the unexpected happens in selfstorage case study top self storage proves why its tops in miami free email updates weekly newsletter premium content information about iss reports digital issues webinars etc featured links •search for   home articles  constructiondevelopmentfinancelegalmanagementmarketingreal estatetechnology  videos resource center  articles by topicblogsdigital issuesgalleriespodcastsreports